                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1429-18480515 t18480515-1429-punishment-235"></join>Confined One Month</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Serjeant.</hi>
